PrecisAmendments to the MEDICAL DEVICES REGULATIONS which remove menstrual tampons having an absorption capacity of 15 grams or less from the Table to Part V (PRE-MARKET REVIEW) and introduce new provisions (Schedule XIV) concerning the labelling of tampons and establishing a standard test method for determining the absorbency capacity of these products.
